    executiveSummary: "Elon Musk's SpaceX is gearing up for its highly anticipated initial public offering (IPO), which is expected to be one of the largest in 2026. The company's valuation is anticipated to exceed $100 billion, with Musk owning approximately 54% of the outstanding shares. SpaceX has already raised over $2 billion in funding and has generated $1.5 billion in revenue from its Starlink satellite internet project.",
